{"tid":165469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亂拋垃圾反徵費係對付擾民政策既唯一出路","createTime":"2017-03-21T11:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T10:16:21.000Z","uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"481ca02e2a45dd76682acff3aeee809c0bc5399c","tid":165469,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"世上無免費午餐，推翻任何暴政都一定要付上代價，正如武裝革命要流血，公民不合作要封路阻人搵食一樣。<br />\n<br />\n今次戰場係環保同公共衛生，最有效方法就係令香港遍地垃圾，嚴重污染，並且明碼實價強迫政府撤回政策局，否則有關情況將永遠持續，同政府目的背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n到時大家只要踏出一步，將屋企垃圾(記得唔好留有個人資料既垃圾)全部放曬係街邊、食環垃圾桶邊、垃圾站附近，甚至路中心、政府合署、黃錦星屋企等就得，呢個方法比勇武抗爭既成本更低，又可以慳錢唔洗益政府同垃圾袋製造商(肯定又係支那公司)，又可以推翻擾民暴政，何樂而不為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497217fb9f3469834ea659ef9a24fb11a7c5f9ae","tid":165469,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"咁都接受唔到既人以後唔好學人講咩抗爭，任人宰割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9618d53d7bfdcd84728eb3f8a80e3db8c5ccf17a","tid":165469,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ace10a9e87db94610ce36057b890b10074af78","tid":165469,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813cd6cc856291ebb89422d072eeb09a054b4586","tid":165469,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"講得好！呢次真係要革命"},{"pid":"1c0e8efbc7adb94cc279669f19e14e3b04e6996c","tid":165469,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"你唔洗講<br />\nd 人都會亂抛垃圾"},{"pid":"a57458db43d62f9cdbd5382dc954a5aa0c5fa86d","tid":165469,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔洗講<br />\nd 人都會亂抛垃圾</b